Finding experiments¶

To use incense we first have to instantiate an experiment loader that will enable us to query the database for specific runs.

QuerySet([Experiment(id=34, name=autoencoder_test), Experiment(id=35, name=autoencoder_test), Experiment(id=36, name=autoencoder_test), Experiment(id=37, name=autoencoder_test), Experiment(id=38, name=autoencoder_test), Experiment(id=39, name=autoencoder_test), Experiment(id=40, name=autoencoder_test), Experiment(id=41, name=autoencoder_test)])
